|               |       AggregateExec: mode=FinalPartitioned, gby=[UserID@0 as UserID, date_part(Utf8("MINUTE"),to_timestamp(hits.EventTime))@1 as date_part(Utf8("MINUTE"),to_timestamp(hits.EventTime)), SearchPhrase@2 as SearchPhrase], aggr=[count(Int64(1))] |
