|               |             AggregateExec: mode=Partial, gby=[UserID@1 as UserID, date_part(MINUTE, to_timestamp(EventTime@0)) as date_part(Utf8("MINUTE"),to_timestamp(hits.EventTime)), SearchPhrase@2 as SearchPhrase], aggr=[count(Int64(1))]                |
